Definition: marked by or capable of arousing controversy
Example: the issue of the death penalty is highly controversial; Rushdie's controversial book; a controversial decision on affirmative action
Synonyms: noun, communication, controversy, UNCONTROVERSIAL, marked, by, or, capable, of, arousing, the, issue, death, penalty, is, highly, controversial, Rushdie, s, book, a, decision, on, affirmative, action
Category: adj.all
